## 1. Project Overview

A full-stack web application that allows government officials and analysts to:

- Monitor startup registrations across India in real time
- Track funding rounds, investment activity, and sector trends
- View state-wise and sector-wise breakdown with visual charts
- Manage startup records (add, edit, delete)
- Generate and download summary reports
- Control access through role-based login/register

