## 3. Roles & Access Levels

Three roles are defined. Each has a different level of access.

| Role | Who | What They Can Do |
|---|---|---|
| `super_admin` | DPIIT HQ Admin | Full access: manage users, all startups, all states, reports |
| `state_officer` | State Nodal Officer | View + manage startups only in their assigned state |
| `viewer` | Analyst / Read-only | View dashboard, charts, reports — no edit/delete |

Role is stored in the `users` table as a string column (`role`).  
Middleware will check role on every protected route.

